This paper deals with the Gaussian Wiretap Channel, which is a topic in Information Theory (cs.IT) and Cryptography (cs.CR). The authors also use tools from Modular Forms, which is a topic in Computational Complexity (cs.CC) and Symbolic Computation (cs.SI). Finally, the study of lattices is a topic in Discrete Mathematics (cs.DS).
